{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GjW9KCcKDhA9439Bs8k6xP","type":"tool_result","content":"    85→\n    86→[Quiz]\n    87→\n    88→Question 1: You've been using AI for years without realizing it. Which of these has been using AI the longest?\n    89→\n    90→A) ChatGPT writing text for you\n    91→B) Your email sorting out spam automatically\n    92→C) A calculator solving math problems\n    93→D) A website remembering your password for you\n    94→\n    95→Correct: B\n    96→\n    97→Explanation: Email spam filters have used machine learning — a type of AI — since the early 2000s. ChatGPT-style conversational AI is much newer (2022 for the public version). Calculators and password managers are regular software, not AI.\n    98→\n    99→---\n   100→\n   101→Question 2: What's the main reason AI feels like it \"just arrived\" even though it's been around for years?\n   102→\n   103→A) AI was kept secret by tech companies until recently\n   104→B) The new AI tools are visible — you interact with them directly — instead of working silently in the background"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f35b7b4d-e00d-4a46-b7f3-fc8a38b8e426","uuid":"dc20bbd9-ad76-4e3b-b380-81c0bd81aeef","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:02:41.924Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/root/clawd/epiphany-learn/content/module-1/lesson-4-ai-in-daily-life.mdx","content":"\n[Quiz]\n\nQuestion 1: You've been using AI for years without realizing it. Which of these has been using AI the longest?\n\nA) ChatGPT writing text for you\nB) Your email sorting out spam automatically\nC) A calculator solving math problems\nD) A website remembering your password for you\n\nCorrect: B\n\nExplanation: Email spam filters have used machine learning — a type of AI — since the early 2000s. ChatGPT-style conversational AI is much newer (2022 for the public version). Calculators and password managers are regular software, not AI.\n\n---\n\nQuestion 2: What's the main reason AI feels like it \"just arrived\" even though it's been around for years?\n\nA) AI was kept secret by tech companies until recently\nB) The new AI tools are visible — you interact with them directly — instead of working silently in the background","numLines":20,"startLine":85,"totalLines":136}}}
