{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MbfwbQWSfEznXZBavwgDvQ","type":"tool_result","content":"    88→\n    89→<RevealCard\n    90→  id=\"q-10\"\n    91→  label=\"10. What integrations do I actually need — and how deep are they?\"\n    92→  reveal=\"Don't ask 'do you integrate with [Tool X]?' — ask to see the integration work in a live demo with real data. Ask: is it bidirectional? Does it handle errors and retries? Is it maintained by the vendor or by a third-party connector service? An integration that breaks silently can corrupt your data without you knowing.\"\n    93→/>\n    94→\n    95→<RevealCard\n    96→  id=\"q-11\"\n    97→  label=\"11. What's your roadmap for the next 6-12 months — and what's guaranteed vs. aspirational?\""}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f35b7b4d-e00d-4a46-b7f3-fc8a38b8e426","uuid":"ef8cdd3f-3d58-4ddc-800e-ba85302ea21b","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:03:36.089Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/root/clawd/epiphany-learn/content/module-5/lesson-3-questions-before-buying.mdx","content":"\n<RevealCard\n  id=\"q-10\"\n  label=\"10. What integrations do I actually need — and how deep are they?\"\n  reveal=\"Don't ask 'do you integrate with [Tool X]?' — ask to see the integration work in a live demo with real data. Ask: is it bidirectional? Does it handle errors and retries? Is it maintained by the vendor or by a third-party connector service? An integration that breaks silently can corrupt your data without you knowing.\"\n/>\n\n<RevealCard\n  id=\"q-11\"\n  label=\"11. What's your roadmap for the next 6-12 months — and what's guaranteed vs. aspirational?\"","numLines":10,"startLine":88,"totalLines":181}}}
